Use a Parameter with a Static Value Type

To update the grouping, click the Widget tab and paste the copied parameter to the dimensionAxis value in columnMap.
Click the Query tab and paste the copied parameter to the orders, groups, and dimensionAxis values.
Save the component.
Edit the dashboard where the component is embedded.
Click the updated component widget and click the Parameters tab.
Click the parameter you created and select Static from the Value Type dropdown menu.
Add a field value in the text box and click Update.
